[thinking] 
[thinking] **Considering class loading in Java**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking about the dynamic instrumentation classes related to JavaTest and whether ExceptionUtils were touched before the test. If `Class#forName` was called but not reported during tests, that could be an issue. If the cache variables were populated beforehand, our public calls might not access the non-populated `class$`.
[thinking] 
