[thinking] 
[thinking] **Evaluating class loading issues**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm considering the problem related to not finding the jar file and receiving a ClassNotFoundException. I’ve checked, and it looks like it did fail. Maybe the NativeImage test has dependencies on the classpath that I haven’t accounted for? Hmm, I don’t really need to know all the details right now. I should look into dynamic class loading test pattern examples to better understand this situation. That might help clarify things!
